snippet.title: Explore the Crown Tundra with the #PokemonSwordShield Expansion Pass!
snippet.description:
https://bit.ly/33aWRVS
Crown Tundra check:

✅ Newly discovered Pokémon
✅ Dynamax Adventures
✅ Pikachu! Wearing! Ash’s! Hats!

Your journey isn’t over yet, Trainers. The second wave of content for the Pokémon Sword Expansion Pass and Pokémon Shield Expansion Pass drops October 22! 

Use of Pokémon Home to transfer Pokémon to or from the Pokémon Sword or Pokémon Shield games may require a persistent internet connection and compatible smart device. Data charges may apply.

Official site: https://www.pokemon.com/SwordShield
Shop: http://www.pokemoncenter.com
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/Pokemon 
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/Pokemon 
Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/pokemon
